quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,5,"Latanaaki …ďee fefindotoo…ďe ganndal maa…óun dalil e ko …ďe nodditii kon immorde e dammbugol …ďi…ó…óo e Alla. Laatanaaki baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe, …ďe …ďe √Īentini …ďen kadi e …óun ganndal, no kaani haa fanti ngol konngol wonungol e yaltude e kunndu…óe ma…ď…ďe ko aldaa e huuturo hakkil, …ďe wowlaali si wanaa konngol fenaande, ngol alaa da∆ī∆īere, alaa ka ngol …ďaarii."
  18,6,"Bela jo'o an -an Nulaa…óo- a tilfay hoore-maa sabu suno e mette, si …ďe hoolaaki ndee Alqur'aanaare, wota a wa…óu, fawaaki ma fewnugol …ďe, anndu ko fawimaa ko yottinngol."
  18,7,"Menen wadi ko woni kon ka kene leydi ndin e tageefooji Ňčari mayri, fii yo Men jarbaade…ďe ko hommbo e ma…ďbe …ďurata mo∆ī∆īinnde golle weltinay…óe Alla, ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe kadi …ďurata bonude golle, fii yo Men yo…ďu mokala ko o hanndi kon e mun."
  18,8,"Menen gom…óii Men wattay ko woni kon ka kene leydi ndin e tageefooji mbullaari yeewundi immore e pu…ói, …óun ko …ďaawo re'ugol ngurndan tageefooji wonu…ói …óin e hoore mayri, yo …ďe tasko …óun."
  18,9,"Wota a sikku -ko an yo Nulaa…óo- wonnde fillayee yim…ďe fammeere nde=wimmba ngo, e alluuje ma…ď…ďe, …óen …óe in…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen winndaa e mun no jeyaa e Aayeeje Amen hawnii…óe …óen. Ko woni ko tanaa majje …ďuri hawnaade yeru tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin."
  18,10,"Annditii an yo Nulaa…óo, tuma nde sukaa…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen moolinoo e diina mun kan …ďe fattoyii, …ďe wi'i e nder noddugol ma…ď…ďe ngol Joomi ma…ď…ďe: "Joomi amen, okku men Hinnayee immorde ka Maa …óun woni haforanaa men bakkatuuji amen, danndaa men ay…ďe e amen, wa…óanaa men fiyaake fergu ngun iwde e keefeeru yaha e gom…óinal feewude faade e laawol Goonga e Peewal."
  18,11,"Refti, …ďaawo yahugol ma…ď…ďe soroya ka fammeere Men wa…ói ka dow noppi ma…ď…ďe wirngallo gaayi nanugol hitooji, Men li…ďi …óoyngol ngol e ma…ď…ďe duu…ďi …óuu…óu…ói."
  18,12,"Refti, …ďaawo …óoyngol ma…ď…ďe juutungol ngol, Men finndini …ďe fii yo Men anndu -Ganndal fen√Īinngol- ko honnde e feddeeji poo…óondiray…ói …óin …ói…ói, fii dummunne √Īii…ďugol ma…ď…ďe ka fammeere, …ďuri anndunde emmbere on dummunne."
  18,13,"Menen, Me…óen ∆īellintine -ko an yo Nulaa…óo- e kumpital fii ma…ď…ďe e Goonga ka sikke alaa e mu'un, …ďen, ko sagataa…ďe gom…óin…ďe Joomi mun, …ďe golliri doftaare Makko, Men …ďeydani …ďe Fewneede e Tabintineede e hoore Goonga."
  18,14,"Men semmbiniri …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen gom…óinal e tabitugol e maggal, e mu√Īanal e dow ferugol ngenndi fii gom…óinal, fewndo …ďe darinoo yeeso lando ngeddo=keefeero on ko …ďe fen√Īin…ďe gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe Alla Kanko tun, …ďe wi'ani mo: " Joomi amen Mo men gom…óini men Rewi On, ko On Jey…óo kammuli …óin e leydi ndin, men rewataa si wonaa Kanko immorde …óin nodditiraa…ói rewatee…óe e hoore fenaande, gom…óii haray men wi'ii -si men rewii tanaa Makko- konngol too√Īungol wo…ó…óitiingol Goonga kan."
  18,15,"Refti yoga ma…ď…ďe ye∆ī∆īitii e yoga hi…ďe wi'a: ∆Āee yim…ďe amen …ďe jogitike gaanin Alla rewetee…ói hi…ďe rewa…ói, kam…ďe …ďe maraa dalil …ďanngu…óo e dewal ma…ď…ďe ngal, alaa hay e gooto …ďur…óo too√Īude ko foti e on fekkindor…óo fenaande o fawi e Alla dammbugol kafidaa…óo e Makko."